Package ApproxsimClient.filter

Interface Summary
ApproxsimObjectAdapter Interface specifying what filter needs to filter adapters of ApproxsimObjects transparantly
 

Class Summary
ActivityFilter ActivityFilter passes objects of Activity type depending on theirs occurence in time.
ActivityResourceFilter ActivityResourceFilter passes objects of Order type depending on the type of their resources.
ActivityTimeFilter ActivityTimeFilter passes objects of Activity type depending on theirs occurence in time.
ChildWithNameAndTypeFilter ChildWithNameAndTypefilter filters out ApproxsimObjects that have a child with a specified name that is of a specified type.
CombinedFilter Combinedfilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning to provided rules.
CombinedORFilter CombinedORFilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning OR rules.
IdentifierFilter Identifierfilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning to provided rules.
IdentifierRegexFilter IdentifierRegexfilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning to provided rules.
MilitaryCodeFilter Passes all objects of type "MilitaryUnit" which have the right code letter on the specified position in the code string.
OrderColorFilter ImageFilter used to convert the color of an order symbol into the color of the orders resource symbol.
PassFilter PassFilter filters passes everything, unless inverted.
PathFilter Pathfilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning to provided rules.
PopulationFilter PopulationFilter filters passes each object of Population type if the number on inhabitants is larger than the given one.
ReferenceFilter This class filters out ApproxsimObjects with respect to their reference.
ApproxsimObjectFilter ApproxsimObjectFilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning to provided rules.
SubtreeFilter This filter passes all the elements in the actual subtree.
TypeFilter Typefilter filters out ApproxsimObjects accordning to provided rules.
